&Scoped-define SELF-NAME slServers
&ANALYZE-SUSPEND _UIB-CODE-BLOCK _CONTROL slServers wWin
ON VALUE-CHANGED OF slServers IN FRAME fMain
DO:
  def var i as int.
  assign slServers.
  iCurrentServer = integer(substring(slServers, 9, 3)).
  do i = 1 to 120:
  slUsers:delete(i) no-error.
  end.
  for each asi._connect where asi._connect._connect-server eq iCurrentServer:
    slUsers:add-last("User: " + string(asi._connect._connect-usr) + "    " 
                     + asi._connect._connect-name).

  end.

END.

